Therefore, under the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act, the Public Health Service Act, and under authority delegated
to the Commissioner of Food and Drugs, it is proposed that 21 CFR parts 20, 310, 312, 314, and 600 be amended as follows:
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=52 g=1 f=4 -->
PART 20_PUBLIC INFORMATION
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=4 -->
1. The authority citation for 21 CFR part 20 continues to read as follows:
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 04 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=4 -->
Authority
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=1 -->
: Secs. 201&hyph;903 of the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act (21 U.S.C. 321&hyph;393); secs. 301, 302, 303, 307,
310, 311, 351, 352, 354&hyph;360F, 361, 362, 1701&hyph;1706, 2101 of the Public Health Service Act (42 U.S.C. 241,
242, 242a, 242l, 242n, 243, 262, 263, 263b&hyph;263n, 264, 265, 300u&hyph;300u&hyph;5, 300aa&hyph;1); 5 U.S.C.
552; 18 U.S.C. 1905. 
