4. Section 310.305 is amended by adding a new sentence at the end of the concluding text of paragraph (a); by revising
paragraphs (b), (c), (d)(3)(ii), and (d)(4); by removing in paragraph (d)(1) the words ``Form FDA&hyph;1639 (Adverse
