<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(j) *&blank;*&blank;* Copies of this guideline may be obtained from the CDER Executive Secretariat Staff (HFD&hyph;8),
Center for Drug Evaluation and Research, Food and Drug Administration, 7500 Standish Pl., Rockville, MD 20857.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

